data.description: Welcome to 2522 Rodman Street.  This property is zoned for 3 units.  This property has dual access from street and alley way.  Currently, this property is Two bedroom, one bath home with large fenced in backyard that could be subdvided.  If buyers do not need the entire backyard, current owner would be willing to reduce the price by $15,000. Also features a nice garage that is accessible from front.  Unfinished basement could be finished to add additional living space.  This home will make someone a nice home or could be used as rental property as well.
